Class Summary
AnalyticItemEvent  
BackgroundEvent This event is posted to the EventBus when the application goes into the background for 2 seconds, or when the application has come back into the foreground.
BeaconRegionEnterEvent This event is posted to the EventBus when the device enters a beacon region.
BeaconRegionExitEvent This event is posted to the EventBus when the device exits a beacon region.
BeaconRegionRangeEvent This event is posted to the EventBus when the device ranges a beacon.
CloudPagesChangedEvent This event is posted to the EventBus when the application has received new CloudPage messages from the server.
GeofenceResponseEvent This event is posted via the EventBus.
LastKnownLocationEvent EventBus low-level sticky notification event that occurs whenever we receive a new location from Android.
LocationUpdateEvent This event is posted via the EventBus.
PowerStatusChangedEvent This event is posted via the EventBus.
PushReceivedEvent This event is posted via the EventBus.
RegistrationEvent This event is posted via the EventBus.
ServerErrorEvent This event is posted via the EventBus.
